{
  "stem": "22047.6",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You see the, the cloud formations and the weather patterns.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And, and this satellite up 22,000 miles sees that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that's what you see on the weather, weather broadcasts on the news programs.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I worked on that one.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I also worked on a communication satellite for Japan, which is now, now doing the same sort of thing over Japan.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Worked there until that contract ran out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And let's see, where did I go?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, I went into-- to other, other contracting efforts at Rocketdyne and Canoga Park and Hughes and El Segundo.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And did a lot of-- my forte being rocket propulsion, they needed consulting in those areas.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I consulted, essentially, until I retired.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In '89-- 1989.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We-- Marge and I formed a, a consulting firm called Marunn, Marge's first name-- first of hers-- her name and the last of my name.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Called it Marunn Consultants, Inc.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] So we worked out of that until I retired in '89.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she continued to do a fair amount of consulting in her field until, oh gosh, she consulted for [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] another four years, I guess.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was really-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] during the war and after the war, I really-- I don't say I didn't have any faith, but I was not heavily involved in, in the religious aspects of life.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We went to church, Presbyterian, when I was married to, to Sally in-- lived in Glendora.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had-- we had moved from North Hollywood to Baldwin Park.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then I had a house built in Glendora, and I lived there while I worked at Aerojet General.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And really, I wasn't-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I had a lot of faith in God.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
